data.description: Welcome to the outstanding gated community of Canyon Lakes at Stonegate. This 5 bedroom includes a game room, media room, vaulted ceilings, cul-de-sac, 2 car garage and island kitchen. The kitchen boasts great countertops, stainless steel appliances and an elegant island. Upstairs you will find four additional bedrooms, game room and media room with risers. As mentioned, the home resides in a cul-de-sac near a beautiful pond. Schedule your tour of this home today. Repairs are needed.
